    <p>
        Welcome to the official web site of the Dee Park Basketball League (DPBL). We established this league in Spring 1998 based on a group of friends who were a part of the student organization Asian American Students In Alliance (AASIA) at the University of Illinois at Chicago (UIC). Many of us had played intramural basketball for several years and with so many of us graduating and moving on the DPBL allowed us to keep in touch as well as to continue playing basketball. The league continued until operations ceased in December 2003. We re-launched in summer of 2010 and are in the midst of our Spring 2017 season. Thank you for your interest and we hope you follow the action throughout the season on this web site.
